[5.010, "o", "\r\n\u001b[2m# PLATFORM TEAM publishes a hardware class — machine type, accelerator, and the GPU's usable memory — plus a cluster that offers it. That published capacity is what the ML team's selectors match against:\u001b[0m\r\n"]
